          Areas of Expertise
        </h2>
        <div class="dimension-line max-w-xs mx-auto"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="technical-border bg-white p-8 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üöÇ</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-blueprint-blue mb-3">
